1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,490
They wanted New York's lights.

2
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:05,150
Brunson wanted the smoke.

3
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:09,830
Heavy is the crown, but Jalen Brunson wore
it like a fitted.

4
00:00:10,420 --> 00:00:14,730
This is not LA, where losing can get
dressed up as lifestyle.

5
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:21,470
This is not Miami, where the crowd shows up late
and leaves before the fourth gets dangerous.

6
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:27,890
This is not Boston, where one day they call
you Jesus and the next day you are Judas.

7
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:30,930
This is New York. This is the Knicks.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:35,270
The Garden can smell fear before the ball
even hits the rim.

9
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:39,190
For years, the biggest names had every
excuse in the book.

10
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,090
The timing was wrong.

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,770
The roster was wrong.

12
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:44,590
The front office was wrong.

13
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:47,510
The pressure was too much. Cool.

14
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,330
Knicks fans heard all of it.

15
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:52,630
As a Knicks fan, it seemed like they were
afraid.

16
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,730
Afraid of the Garden turning on them.

17
00:00:54,780 --> 00:00:56,970
Afraid of the back page.

18
00:00:57,520 --> 00:01:02,510
Afraid of coming to New York, failing, and
having New Yorkers remind them forever.

19
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:04,970
They wanted New York's lights.

20
00:01:05,340 --> 00:01:07,530
They did not want New York's smoke.

21
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:09,270
And Brooklyn?

22
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,690
Brooklyn is not the Knicks.

23
00:01:10,740 --> 00:01:12,690
The Nets are not even the little brother.

24
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,690
They are the distant relative.

25
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,010
Same city. Different weight.

26
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:20,610
You can hoop in New York without carrying
New York.

27
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,310
The Knicks are different.

28
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,810
The Garden is different.

29
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:26,030
That orange and blue is different.

30
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:29,530
And Brunson knew that. He chose it anyway.

31
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:32,170
Read or listen to the full essay.

32
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:35,970
Heavy Is The Crown. Brunson Wanted The
Smoke.

